        "client_msg_id": "c5ea0417-cf18-4d94-a5d6-20295b88df15",
        "text": "is there a reason to keep ancient references in the base-defunct.Rd file?\n\nI see Sys.putenv (removed 15 years ago), getenv (ditto), real\/as.real (removed for 3.0.0).\n\nKeeping functions still available but marked .Defunct() makes sense to me, but why retain the reference after it's totally removed?",
