        "client_msg_id": "a568b636-181d-4b0e-9980-10a72f933d50",
        "text": "to me the NEWS is the place to keep that sort of \"permanent documentation\". should we expect every object that R has ever exported to keep accumulating in that file? what about distinguishing \"marked .Defunct\" and \"fully removed\"? (is there a meaningful difference?)",
