    {
        "user": "U081Z9041A5",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1774291303.029559",
        "client_msg_id": "c5aebcbd-50de-4388-9fc8-c148be9eec8b",
        "text": "As Lawrence Lessig once wrote, \"Code Is Law\".  I also grep in sources because we all know that documentation may lag. That is also why my sympathy lies with keeping such declarations: the net benefit (of having them discoverable) outweighs the near-zero cost of keeping them around.",
